duties_responsibilities.duty: Manage and oversee high-end residential, restaurant, retail, and historical projects, ensuring timely and successful completion.
Utilize working knowledge of building department permit processing to facilitate project approvals and compliance.
Coordinate with architects, engineers, and subcontractors to ensure project progress and quality standards.
Ensure compliance with construction codes, regulations, and industry standards.
Proficiently use AutoCAD, Sketch-UP, Photoshop, InDesign, and MS Office to support project design and documentation.
Manage project timelines, budgets, and resources effectively to meet client expectations and firm profitability.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor's degree in Architecture (BArch) or Master's degree in Architecture (MArch)
Working knowledge of building department permit processing
